# Rasm Rhino Categories

Read `libs/csharp/Rasm.Rhino/AGENTS.md`, `libs/csharp/AGENTS.md`, `.claude/skills/coding-csharp/SKILL.md`, and local RhinoWIP XML/decompile evidence before naming Rhino APIs.

## Category Owners

| [INDEX] | [FOLDER]        |
| :-----: | --------------- |
|   [1]   | `Commands/`     |
|   [2]   | `Capture/`      |
|   [3]   | `Construction/` |
|   [4]   | `Exchange/`     |
|   [5]   | `Camera/`       |
